                "caption": "Figure 2:Remote sensing composed image retrieval for disaster monitoring.We restructure xView2[41]into a composed retrieval setting where a query consists of apre-eventreference imageof a specific location and atextual modifierdescribing the desired post-event state (e.g.,post-hurricane). For each disaster type (a–f), we illustrate the query and the corresponding relevance criterion:positivesare images of thesame scene/locationdepicting the specified post-event state, whilenegativesare non-matching candidates (e.g., different locations with the target change or the same location without the target change).",
